用貞子題材，但反應差天共地。<br />\n真係出不逢時"},{"pid":"ea644773a207dcc3a3bd6ea5d1dfab54e34588e3","tid":130624,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T02:20:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會唔會因為有其他人作左，所以我出都會冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我記得以前高登睇過，但係唔記得係咪巴打你作<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">之後係咪有富剛出黎個個</span></blockquote><br />\n係，</blockquote><br />\n咁睇黎都好多年前了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n三，四年前啦"},{"pid":"ed1f2fe61d38322b80618e1414258f76ce54c4be","tid":130624,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T02:22:01.000Z","msg":"所以實會有人覺得我抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35fae12cc2f9d67e90d7e62a645a76c92f778486","tid":130624,"uid":63345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T02:46:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無原版睇</blockquote><br />\n有，紙言</blockquote><br />\n有無link, 我剩係search到你而家呢個重制版"},{"pid":"a04b8bfeb8df85b96318f8cc7768ccfd3cd13f91","tid":130624,"uid":60935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T02:54:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以實會有人覺得我抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁又唔會既，兩套我都有睇，雖然都係講愛情，但係唔相似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe95a62fc5b998c552a6460751ae51cf7ced2da","tid":130624,"uid":21305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T03:03:47.000Z","msg":"果邊都完左, 唔怕既 加油"},{"pid":"c82fb981b619297eb5bac947f75abb84a32088b8","tid":130624,"uid":58950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T03:18:58.000Z","msg":"等文睇"},{"pid":"4fdb8d3c8e0de161a589a8e9116e3e0b85aac832","tid":130624,"uid":2835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T03:34:18.000Z","msg":"你呢套貞子故我記得最後係好似有兩個ending?"},{"pid":"64c05affee23c948c7b5dcc155470ea8870266b6","tid":130624,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T05:05:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無原版睇</blockquote><br />\n有，紙言</blockquote><br />\n有無link, 我剩係search到你而家呢個重制版</blockquote><br />\n其實個個冇重製，係原版。"},{"pid":"d2224201f7fa4eb57ed29d470ddb37fd2e52f2b4","tid":130624,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T05:06:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>果邊都完左, 唔怕既 加油</blockquote><br />\n好既，今晚收工先更新"},{"pid":"5e068e9657a301deaff190e3179b633862b1f8ea","tid":130624,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T05:07:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你呢套貞子故我記得最後係好似有兩個ending?</blockquote><br />\n係三個"},{"pid":"fc0ea53183c407ea7f87efd34d30ade748ab5136","tid":130624,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T05:07:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等文睇</blockquote><br />\n麻煩等待，要今晚繼續，番緊工"},{"pid":"ceebdaee5451dec417d7179eb545ee3aeba314ef","tid":130624,"uid":63345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T05:16:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無原版睇</blockquote><br />\n有，紙言</blockquote><br />\n有無link, 我剩係search到你而家呢個重制版</blockquote><br />\n其實個個冇重製，係原版。</blockquote><br />\n得2個chapter咁少既"},{"pid":"05c4a231d9dd35da18eaaf7f3edd367f205b40a2","tid":130624,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T06:03:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無原版睇</blockquote><br />\n有，紙言</blockquote><br />\n有無link, 我剩係search到你而家呢個重制版</blockquote><br />\n其實個個冇重製，係原版。</blockquote><br />\n得2個chapter咁少既</blockquote><br />\n之前收起左，而家去開番"},{"pid":"44febe753ee7183b6347924533fba4fcdce2aa0a","tid":130624,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:05:08.000Z","msg":"「貞子，你肚唔肚餓啊，我煮個拉麵比你食啊。成日係個井到，冇好野食<br />\n<br />\n過。」」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我打算前去廚房，還未到門口，眼前已經有一把把刀於半空等待著我。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「唔好扮晒好心，我知你想打發我走。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n她輕嘆一聲然後轉身，似乎想回到電視機裡，我上前拉著她，她的手十分冰<br />\n<br />\n冷。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n「你做咩？放手......」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「你任務未完成，唔係要殺我咩？ 」我說。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 「唔好迫我殺人。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 「「咁其實你唔係諗住殺我，係我屋企走黎走去做咩？唔通真係想住啊？<br />\n<br />\n問。只係你迫自已，就係因為一直留係個井裡，身處係灰暗環境鎖住自已，放<br />\n<br />\n唔開。正所謂坐這井，望那天，一事無成。你應該離開電視機既世界，再學做<br />\n<br />\n人類。如果唔介意既，真係給比我七日既時間，等你去重拾人類既幸福 ，重<br />\n<br />\n新認識世界。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n她低下頭，一臉無奈說道：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「我鬼黎......點解你可以唔驚我？仲可以咁多野講，係你之前，我已經嚇死左好多人......」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「我真係好彩，我有心跳問題，你都嚇我唔死，咁就由我開始，唔再死人好唔<br />\n<br />\n好？」我說。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「其實嚇你唔死係有原因，我一直想搵到個有勇氣既人可以幫我，亦需要一間安全屋......」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫忙？安全屋？強大的貞子應該沒有甚麼對手吧？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我不知道她的打算，現在對她已經不像起初般恐懼，細看她的臉孔，只是裝兇<br />\n<br />\n惡而己，一個有超能力的日本女子。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在貞子前傳中，她本來就是個善良單純的可憐人，有理想有愛人，因世俗不接<br />\n<br />\n受，而將她迫成惡魔。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n她接著說：<br />\n<br />\n「我知道你諗咩，唔使可憐我，暫時解釋唔到比你聽咩事住。只係我搵到個合<br />\n<br />\n適既地方留七日，希望七日後大家冇事，你驚唔驚？到時你可能真係會死。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「係咪姐係哈利波特入面咁，哈利波特啊媽既保護咒，佢成年之前個七年只要<br />\n<br />\n番姨丈屋企就會冇事？」"},{"pid":"adf80744d08b975669815309e86e119fd0e980e5","tid":130624,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:34:13.000Z","msg":"今次重製，唔只係愛情約會，係加入D日本妖怪傳說，之前版本都有D妖怪出過場，仲有係二次大戰，日本軍人做實驗，貞子同佢母親既情節。"},{"pid":"f91edad50af39065b8f972796823d87030becb2e","tid":130624,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T16:10:45.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"6f250c73ca174ad111b2b48f33d066ae58bb476b","tid":130624,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T16:45:00.000Z","msg":"訓前一推，聽日可以下午出"},{"pid":"bb68a855788740ab4198398bc3909a42d8bcb042","tid":130624,"uid":70331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T02:29:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://lohas.nicoseiga.jp/thumb/2040887i?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flohas.nicoseiga.jp%2Fthumb%2F2040887i%3F&h=51c69d65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n偷圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"f934ce7f97a7670a79e217744eff1c63e7bf5e53","tid":130624,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T03:46:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://lohas.nicoseiga.jp/thumb/2040887i?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flohas.nicoseiga.jp%2Fthumb%2F2040887i%3F&h=51c69d65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n偷圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?</blockquote><br />\n哩張圖唔係我整，以前揾張晨幫我"},{"pid":"a8c8469d32201be3b06d0722989c56246437ad68","tid":130624,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T03:49:43.000Z","msg":"負評既人，對我公平咩?<br />\n<br />\n人地作貞子就咁多正評，仲要係寫個時有睇過我個故"},{"pid":"b5fea6cd7271573e4c66a80d452a6fa271b1f3aa","tid":130624,"uid":70267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T04:04:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>負評既人，對我公平咩?<br />\n<br />\n人地作貞子就咁多正評，仲要係寫個時有睇過我個故</blockquote><br />\n好公平<br />\n人地係作得好過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c73e5ad7cc267ece646f10cc90b02523e4e6f071","tid":130624,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T04:08:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>負評既人，對我公平咩?<br />\n<br />\n人地作貞子就咁多正評，仲要係寫個時有睇過我個故</blockquote><br />\n好公平<br />\n人地係作得好過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nok,咁繼續比負評"},{"pid":"05fbdc27d587c2fd6538b619fe2205e86f328c6c","tid":130624,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T05:50:31.000Z","msg":"我唔係話自己寫得好，但係換個情況，想呻句公平咩好正常。以前係高登出哩個作品個時好多人睇，都唔係而家咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地啲fans一黎就又話偷圖又盛，比負評。"},{"pid":"8c8e6fe83f8e3ce64f677bb70d42557f8033b6a4","tid":130624,"uid":70892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T06:01:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我唔係話自己寫得好，但係換個情況，想呻句公平咩好正常。以前係高登出哩個作品個時好多人睇，都唔係而家咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地啲fans一黎就又話偷圖又盛，比負評。</blockquote><br />\n你上一頁話自己寫不逢時<br />\n我想講你衣家出文先係錯哂timing<br />\n海藍巴個故岩岩先完<br />\n邊有咁快抽離到出黎接受你個故"},{"pid":"12a7185377d952808914d32d2c3620792dfe8d25","tid":130624,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T06:11:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我唔係話自己寫得好，但係換個情況，想呻句公平咩好正常。以前係高登出哩個作品個時好多人睇，都唔係而家咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地啲fans一黎就又話偷圖又盛，比負評。</blockquote><br />\n你上一頁話自己寫不逢時<br />\n我想講你衣家出文先係錯哂timing<br />\n海藍巴個故岩岩先完<br />\n邊有咁快抽離到出黎接受你個故</blockquote><br />\n當初冇太諗過因為佢而家寫左，對我出哩方面有影響，純粹將啲舊故擺上黎。"},{"pid":"a2ecef197414856286f140e1b5d1c5747cea118a","tid":130624,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T07:15:43.000Z","msg":"既然係唔接受既結果，咁我都係寫番其它故"},{"pid":"bf857b37d302a784cc6ee15d6453f96149feb0ab","tid":130624,"uid":10821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T07:29:52.000Z","msg":"唔好丫 我想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0cd62dba27bcdc100b15ac0fd88be6bcb16f058","tid":130624,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T10:23:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好丫 我想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想加油，但而家咁情況係繼續出都難堪，有眼見，只會越多人笑同負評"},{"pid":"c77e27e6a04deba705a3790e9c49f0b55559de2e","tid":130624,"uid":52961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T12:29:47.000Z","msg":"樓主唔好介意人地點講點睇 做返想做既野咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然我都睇過海巴個故 但我覺得都寫得唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望你繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aded802a3355e7529cc0048527f4b5d5273752eb","tid":130624,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T12:39:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主唔好介意人地點講點睇 做返想做既野咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然我都睇過海巴個故 但我覺得都寫得唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望你繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已經係開咩故都係咁比架啦，所以而家開始幾多負皮都好，我唔再理，會繼續作。"},{"pid":"ba4a71baaae53538c21fa9fc423de25f3208311a","tid":130624,"uid":29898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T12:41:17.000Z","msg":"無睇清楚係講故台<br />\n( Show Blocked User - 沈默言 )"},{"pid":"43a5eece33f662ac2605a2fe461b6379ed6db5fe","tid":130624,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T12:41:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無睇清楚係講故台<br />\n( Show Blocked User - 沈默言 )</blockquote><br />\n下？"},{"pid":"b44b4149e2e9383a96725d632e188a09d9e7fdf4","tid":130624,"uid":6572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T14:33:47.000Z","msg":"樓主你個故都有一定嘅年齡啦喎，不過無諗過你會係呢度再寫過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a48ee88c66ab9879be88264cd0a800f106d48562","tid":130624,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T14:38:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主你個故都有一定嘅年齡啦喎，不過無諗過你會係呢度再寫過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，覺得D情節得愛情太悶，可以發展多D<br />\n不過無諗過我唔開心講句都比人D FANS話"},{"pid":"d81b507539f60dab279a660b82e0571139956e8f","tid":130624,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T07:24:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主你個故都有一定嘅年齡啦喎，不過無諗過你會係呢度再寫過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，覺得D情節得愛情太悶，可以發展多D<br />\n不過無諗過我唔開心講句都比人D FANS話</blockquote><br />\n而點解我要唔開心，係因為對方話自己作個時，係有睇我既故。雖然唔會完全一樣，但或多或少都影響，係哩方面再加多啲佢自己諗既情節。<br />\n你地啲fans 本未倒置，走黎比說話我聽"}]}